CLAY MASK  is an essential part of my Summer Skincare Routine. The best part about Clay Masks is that has the ability is to draw out excess oil, dirt and impurities from the skin’s surface and should be an integral part of the everyone's summer beauty regimen.

The @ikkai.beauty Fruity Surprise Face Mask is enriched with - 
🫐 BLUEBERRY EXTRACTS -  rich in antioxidants, has anti-inflammatory properties that help heal acne and resist premature skin aging. 
🫐 VITAMIN E - One of the richest ingredients for skincare, Vitamin E protects your skin against sun damage and neutralizes free radicals. It has a healing and moisturizing impact that strengthens the skin barrier function.
🫐 NIACINAMIDE - A potent active that helps heal skin inflammation and fights pigmentation and open pores. Niacinamide is suitable for all skin types that helps even out skin tone and revive your skin’s youthful glow.

✨ Apply an even layer on Clean Dry Skin 
✨ Leave it on for 10 mins 
✨ Rinse it off 
✨ It absorbed all the excess oil from my skin without drying it out too much.
✨ And post application my skin was glowing and felt soft and nourished.
✨ Maintains skin’s youthfulness
✨ Minimises pores and fights pigmentation.
✨ Also, a bonus, it smells DEVINE 😍

latestIgtvVideos.title: HOW TO USE YOUR SKINCARE PRODUCTS ft. @theearthrhythm 🖤
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
We will be talking about 3 @theearthrhythm products today. ✌🏽️

🌀SUPERFOOD FACE MASQUE WITH BLUE SPIRULINA

🧜🏽‍♂️ Apply a thin layer of the mask onto your cleansed face. 
🧜🏽‍♂️ Leave it on 15-20 mins and relax. 
🧜🏽‍♂️ Then wash it off with water, and pat dry your face with a soft towel. 
🧜🏽‍♂️ Do not scrub off the mask without water.

🌀 2% ALPHA ARBUTIN + HYALURONIC ACID - SKIN CLARIFYING SERUM

🧜🏽‍♂️ Apply a few drops to your DRY face in the AM and PM routine. 
🧜🏽‍♂️ Use it before the moisturiser.
🧜🏽‍♂️ Remember to use Sun Protection in the AM 
🧜🏽‍♂️ To boost its benefits, apply it alongside your Vitamin C, or after exfoliating with an AHA (which will improve its absorption) 
🧜🏽‍♂️ Since, it also has Hyaluronic Acid in it, it is important to follow it up with a Moisturiser 

🌀 PHYTO-CERAMIDE DEEP MOISTURISER

🧜🏽‍♂️ Apply this moisturiser on face and neck after cleansing, toning, exfoliating and after using your serum.
🧜🏽‍♂️ For best results, use both day and night on damp skin. 

▪️ Individual Reviews of these products will be available on my page very soon.

latestIgtvVideos.title: 3 SIMPLE STEPS MORNING SKINCARE ROUTINE
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
STEP 1 - USE A GENTLE CLEANSER/FACE WASH

Product Recommendation - Episoft Cleansing Lotion is a great choice for morning cleanser. @episoftofficial 

( During Winters I skip my morning cleanse as it makes my skin dry) 

STEP 2 - VITAMIN C Based Products 

Product Used - @goodal_india Green Tangerine Vita C Dark Spot Serum and Green Tangerine Vita C Cream available at @maccaron_beauty and @daisy.on.ig (Use Code - TAABS10 for 10% OFF)

I take a little amount of my @goodal_india Vita C Cream on my hands and get 2-3 drops of the Goodal Vita C Dark Spot Serum for better absorption and results.

▪️You don't necessarily have to use a Vitamin C based cream, you can use any Moisturiser of your choice.

STEP 3 - SUNSCREEN

Product Used - @neutrogena.india ULTRA SHEER SUNSCREEN. 

I use 2 FINGER RULE when I'm indoors and use 3 FINGER RULE when I have to head outdoors. 
Remember to Reapply Your Sunscreen Every 2-3 hours.
